=== Array Stress Tests ===

--- Large Array Creation ---
Build 100-elem array (push): 0ms
Build 1000-elem array (push): 2ms
Build 5000-elem array (push): 7ms

--- Array Iteration ---
for-i loop 1000 elems: 2ms (sum=499500)
for-of loop 1000 elems: 1ms
forEach 1000 elems: 2ms

--- Map/Filter/Reduce ---
map 1000 elems: 0ms
filter 1000 elems: 1ms
reduce 1000 elems: 0ms
map 100 elems x100: 2ms
filter 100 elems x100: 1ms
reduce 100 elems x100: 10ms

--- Chained Operations ---
map-filter-map chain: 0ms
filter-map-reduce x50: 7ms

--- Sorting ---
sort 100 elems x100: 73ms
sort 1000 elems x20: 147ms

--- Search Operations ---
find middle (1000 elems x500): 28ms
includes middle (1000 elems x500): 3ms
indexOf middle (1000 elems x500): 3ms
some (1000 elems x500): 29ms
every (1000 elems x500): 56ms

--- Splice/Slice ---
splice insert (100 elems x1000): 4ms
splice delete (100 elems x1000): 4ms
slice (100 elems x1000): 3ms

--- Concat/Spread ---
concat 50+50 x1000: 3ms
spread 50+50 x1000: 3ms

--- Flat/FlatMap ---
flat (5x2) x2000: 4ms
map+flat (100 elems) x500: 54ms

--- Array of Objects ---
filter objects (100 objs x200): 6ms
map to property (100 objs x200): 7ms
find by property (100 objs x200): 9ms
sort by property (100 objs x50): 7ms

